{"tid":167753,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下sun mobile 新個個5gb會員plan","createTime":"2017-03-23T05:14:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T10:48:31.000Z","uid":53201,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b49c87ebb161f6d6a5672892365693e3aa53a7e4","tid":167753,"uid":53201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:14:59.000Z","msg":"於2017年3月期間到電訊數碼SUN Mobile 門市登記成為The Club會員，即可以同樣月費$96升級使用高速4G 21Mbps 數據服務計劃。每月首5GB最高下載速度 21Mbps，其後本地流動數據網絡規格將會被降至上限128kbps，承諾期12個月。詳情請瀏覽 <a href=\"http://sunmobile.com.hk/ad_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsunmobile.com.hk%2Fad_news&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=3a6afd34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sunmobile.com.hk/ad_news</a> 。受條款及細則約束。查詢/取消77771010<br />\n<br />\n* 此SUN Mobile「The Club尊享 - 4G隨意用數據服務計劃加強版」由新移動通訊有限公司提供。此服務計劃月費原價為$108，The Club會員可享首12個月每月$30月費折扣優惠，另須繳付每月$18之港鐵/隧道/流動電訊牌照/行政費；唯此服務費消費將不會賺取The Club會員積分。選用此服務計劃，須簽訂12個月承諾期。 <br />\n<br />\n^ 5GB本地流動數據量只適用於攜號轉台客戶：每月首5GB之網絡規格最高下載速度為21Mbps，其後本地流動數據網絡規格將會被降至上限128kbps。新號碼客戶：每月首3GB之網絡規格最高下載速度為21Mbps，其後本地流動數據網絡規格將會被降至上限128kbps。實際速度會相當地少於最高下載速度，並會因應不同因素而有所偏差，包括互聯網之實際情況、伺服器運作速度、網絡性能、覆蓋範圍、地點、所使用之電腦或裝置、硬件、軟件及其他因素。如有任何爭議，SUN Mobile保留最終決定權。此計劃另包括3000分鐘本地話音通話。受其他條款及細則約束。如欲終止服務你可於最少30日前通知本公司。然而，若於承諾期之前終止合約，你須支付於申請書上所列明之服務提早終止費用，所有剩餘之回贈及已預繳之費用將不會被退回。有關產品、服務計劃、優惠及有關條款及細則，<a href=\"http://詳情請瀏覽www.sunmobile.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%A9%B3%E6%83%85%E8%AB%8B%E7%80%8F%E8%A6%BDwww.sunmobile.com.hk&d=HXPWCXSY8fSkht0R8v8uOSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=805eb2bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">詳情請瀏覽www.sunmobile.com.hk</a>。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似太過旬？呢家用緊呢個台既88$無限上網plan, 每個月有2gb 但過左之後個網速得128kbps <br />\n但佢呢個新plan 有5gb 之外最高有21mbps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n價錢仲要差唔遠 大家點睇？"},{"pid":"3bccd2747e3217ac43e865bf38f231c45e4ae63c","tid":167753,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:21:45.000Z","msg":"去電訊台問啦"},{"pid":"504b5af7a8f6316b749452e89d8db5db09f84c5e","tid":167753,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"我用緊 都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4304bf55c4ddccc002de31edf6f8825f24ce8736","tid":167753,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T05:26:58.000Z","msg":"地鐵超唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9992a67f0415faffbe5941ba77fc1819ba469f2e","tid":167753,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T06:27:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地鐵超唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地鐵無邊間掂"},{"pid":"bd8e75ec9dd897f470fa5b20a79fba1d5b75794c","tid":167753,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T07:07:11.000Z","msg":"入隧道頭果幾分鐘都唔掂<br />\n之後係面書load片都叫流暢"},{"pid":"f3da0d88a9de8215d24803c92f2e04f85b785250","tid":167753,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:38:47.000Z","msg":"岩岩續咗呢個plan<br />\n想問下點登入the club?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3db818690db6bba17a0fa8d13b9e1724f6e7543e","tid":167753,"uid":75358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"開頭好撚快 之後鎖128慢到仆直 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0661bf57e11c35fd45f484118e86dd0fe128a4fe","tid":167753,"uid":90577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開頭好撚快 之後鎖128慢到仆直 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n由MB變KB,你想幾快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}